e%2070-year-old%20will%20take%20over%20as%20the%20non-executive%20chairman%20of%20the%20%241%20trillion%20(around%20Rs%2086.55%20lakh%20crore)%20business%20empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2094-year-old%20billionaire%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhoward-buffett-succession-berkshire-hathaway-72b2caa7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20revealed%20that%20nearly%20all%20of%20his%20remaining%20wealth%20will%20be%20directed%20to%20a%20new%20charitable%20trust.%20Mr%20Buffett%2C%20who%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bplanning%20for%20decades%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20transition%2C%20has%20ensured%20that%20his%20three%20children%20-%20Susie%2C%20Howard%2C%20and%20Peter%20-%20will%20not%20inherit%20the%20bulk%20of%20his%20fortune%20but%20will%20instead%20manage%20the%20new%20trust.%20The%20trio%20will%20oversee%20%24140%20billion%20worth%20of%20Berkshire%20stocks%20dedicated%20to%20philanthropic%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20choosing%20Howie%20as%20successor%2C%20Mr%20Buffet%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20getting%20it%20because%20he's%20my%20son.%20I'm%20very%2C%20very%2C%20very%20lucky%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20trust%20all%20three%20of%20my%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowie%2C%20who%20has%20served%20as%20a%20director%20on%20Berkshire's%20board%20for%20over%2030%20years%2C%20said%20he%20feels%20ready%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20I'm%20prepared%20for%20it%20because%20he%20prepared%20me.%20That's%20a%20lot%20of%20years%20of%20influence%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20years%20of%20teaching%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20WSJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Howie%20Buffet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHowie%20Buffett%20struggled%20during%20his%20college%20years%20but%20eventually%20found%20his%20footing%20with%20guidance%20from%20his%20father%2C%20a%20WSJ%20report%20said.%20On%20Warren%20Buffett's%20advice%2C%20Howie%20moved%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20work%20at%20See's%20Candies%2C%20a%20company%20owned%20by%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20to%20gain%20practical%20business%20experience.%20He%20later%20started%20his%20own%20excavating%20business%20before%20transitioning%20to%20farming.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWarren%20Buffett%20purchased%20a%20farm%20for%20Howie%2C%20who%20paid%20his%20father%20market-rate%20rent%20to%20operate%20it%2C%20as%20per%20WSJ.%20Over%20time%2C%20Howie%20became%20a%20strong%20advocate%20for%20no-till%20farming%2C%20focusing%20on%20soil%20conservation%20and%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%201989%2C%20Howie%20Buffet%20joined%20the%20county%20board%20of%20commissioners%20and%20later%20became%20a%20member%2C%20and%20eventually%20chairman%2C%20of%20the%20Nebraska%20ethanol%20board.%20From%202017%20to%202018%2C%20he%20served%20as%20sheriff%20of%20Macon%20County%2C%20Illinois%2C%20following%20his%20earlier%20role%20as%20an%20auxiliary%20deputy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESince%201993%2C%20Howie%20Buffet%20has%20served%20as%20a%20director%20on%20the%20boards%20of%20several%20prominent%20companies%2C%20including%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20Coca-Cola%20Enterprises%2C%20Lindsay%20Corporation%2C%20Sloan%20Implement%2C%20ConAgra%20Foods%2C%20and%20agricultural%20equipment-maker%20GSI%20Group.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHowie%20Buffet%20established%20a%20charitable%20foundation%20focused%20on%20conservation%20and%20other%20philanthropic%20initiatives.%20He%20has%20also%20authored%20eight%20books%20on%20conservation%2C%20wildlife%2C%20and%20related%20topics.%20Howie%20Buffett%20married%20Devon%20Morse%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20has%20a%20son%2C%20Howard%20Warren%20Buffett.%20He%20also%20had%20four%20stepdaughters%20from%20his%20marriage%20to%20Morse.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736839440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fa2p6oi68_howard-buffett_625x300_