2C%20Anand%20Akharas%20Take%20'Amrit%20Snan'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Naga%20sadhus%20of%20the%20Niranjani%20and%20Anand%20Akharas%20arrived%20for%20'Amrit%20Snan'%20at%20Maha%20Kumbh%20on%20the%20auspicious%20occasion%20of%20Makar%20Sankranti.%20Anand%20Akhada%20Acharya%20Mandleswar%20Balkanand%20ji%20Maharaj%20led%20the%20processions%20along%20with%20Surendra%20Giri%20ji%20Maharaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpiritual%20leader%20Swami%20Kailashanand%20Giri%20led%20the%20processions%20of%20the%20Niranjani%20Akhara%20for%20the%20first%20Amrit%20Snan%20of%20Maha%20Kumbh%20on%20the%20auspicious%20occasion%20of%20Makar%20Sankranti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenowned%20for%20its%20emphasis%20on%20yoga%2C%20meditation%2C%20and%20the%20pursuit%20of%20spiritual%20knowledge%2C%20Niranjani%20Akhara%20is%20one%20of%20the%20significant%20Akharas%20that%20participate%20in%20this%20sacred%20gathering.%20The%20teachings%20focus%20on%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20inner%20exploration%2C%20guiding%20practitioners%20toward%20spiritual%20awakening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20Akhada%20worships%20Suryanarayana%2C%20the%20Sun%20God%2C%20as%20their%20presiding%20deity.%20The%20Akhada%20is%20also%20known%20for%20setting%20up%20educational%20institutions%20that%20teach%20Hindu%20scriptures%2C%20yoga%2C%20meditation%2C%20and%20martial%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sadhus%20of%20the%2013%20akhadas%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharm%20will%20take%20a%20holy%20dip%20at%20Triveni%20Sangam%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2013%20akhadas%20are%20divided%20into%20three%20groups%20--%20Sanyasi%20(Shaivite)%2C%20Bairagi%20(Vaishnav)%20and%20Udaseen.%20The%20Shaivite%20akhadas%20include%20Shree%20Panch%20Dashnam%20Juna%20Akhada%2C%20Shree%20Panchayati%20Akhada%20Niranjani%2C%20Shree%20Shambhu%20Panchayati%20Atal%20Akhada%2C%20Shree%20Panchayati%20Akhada%20Mahanirvani%2CShree%20Shambhu%20Panchagni%20Akhada%2C%20Shree%20Panchdashnam%20Aavahan%20Akhada%20and%20Taponidhi%20Shri%20Anand%20Akhada%20Panchayti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Kumar%20Swami%20Ji%20Maharaj%20from%20Anand%20Akhara%20expressed%20his%20happiness%20and%20said%20that%20nothing%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20bigger%20than%20this%20(Mahakumbh).%20Those%20who%20are%20able%20to%20come%20here%20are%20extremely%20fortunate...%20Wherever%20we%20see%20people%20are%20fighting%20among%20themselves.%20Here%20it's%20peaceful.%20Merely%20being%20present%20here%20and%20watching%20everything%20unfold%2C%20brings%20joy%20and%20peace...%20Our%20saints%20and%20shastras%20have%20always%20wanted%20peace%20in%20the%20world.%20I%20bow%20down%20to%20our%20great%20seers%20and%20our%20religious%20texts%2C%20I%20bow%20down%20to%20our%20earth%20and%20Lord%20Shiva%20for%20giving%20us%20this%20day.%20Everyone%20should%20come%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaha%20Kumbh%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20significant%20religious%20congregation%20in%20the%20world%2C%20held%20every%2012%20years%20at%20one%20of%20four%20locations%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Kumbh-2025%2C%20which%20is%20Poorna%20Kumbh%20will%20take%20place%20till%20February%2026%2C%202025.%20Key%20'snan'%20dates%20include%20January%2014%20(Makar%20Sankranti%20-%20First%20Shahi%20Snan)%2C%20January%2029%20(Mauni%20Amavasya%20-%20Second%20Shahi%20Snan)%2C%20February%203%20(Basant%20Panchami%20-%20Third%20Shahi%20Snan)%2C%20February%2012%20(Maghi%20Purnima)%2C%20and%20February%2026%20(Maha%20Shivaratri).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736838240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fkfehjdlo_mahakumbh_625x300_14_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-maha-kumbh-naga-sadhus-of-niranjani-anan