id%20in%20an%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20minister%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20petition%20by%20seven%20BJP%20MPs%2C%20seeking%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20central%20scheme.%20In%20his%20response%2C%20he%20has%20said%20that%20the%20petition%2C%20%26quot%3Bostensibly%20filed%20as%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%2C%20is%20nothing%20else%20but%20a%20politically%20motivated%20petition%2C%20filed%20in%20view%20of%20the%20ensuing%20elections%20to%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20Delhi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioners%20are%20political%20persons%2C%20who%20belong%20to%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20said%20political%20party%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20impose%20its%20wishes%20on%20Delhi%2C%20even%20though%20they%20were%20able%20to%20win%20only%2010%25%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20last%20election%20to%20the%20legislative%20assembly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20minister%20said%20the%20petition%20sings%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%20praises%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Centre's%20scheme%20but%20does%20not%20mention%20the%20policies%20currently%20in%20force%20in%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BThe%20omission%20is%20deliberate%20in%20as%20much%20as%20had%20any%20such%20comparison%20been%20done%20between%20the%20scheme%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20and%20the%20various%20schemes%20already%20being%20implemented%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Government%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20evident%20that%20the%20schemes%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Government%20are%20far%20superior%20to%20the%20scheme%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20if%20the%20schemes%20in%20place%20in%20the%20capital%20are%20substituted%20by%20the%20Centre's%20scheme%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20be%20a%20loss%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20Delhi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20policymaking%20is%20the%20exclusive%20domain%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20it%20is%20settled%20law%20that%20no%20court%20will%20enter%20the%20domain%20of%20framing%20of%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAB-PMJAY%20scheme%20is%20unsuitable%20for%20meeting%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20The%20said%20scheme%20has%20been%20framed%20by%20the%20Central%20Government%20based%20upon%20the%20material%20and%20data%20available%20with%20them.%20The%20AB-PMJAY%20scheme%20is%20based%20upon%20the%20estimation%20of%20the%20Central%20Government.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20federal%20structure%20in%20India%2C%20it%20is%20not%20mandatory%20for%20every%20political%20unit%20to%20follow%20the%20policy%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%20particularly%20when%20the%20schemes%20and%20the%20policies%20already%20in%20operation%20and%20functioning%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Delhi%20are%20far%20superior%20to%20the%20AB-PMJAY%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20had%20used%202011%20Census%20data%20for%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme.%20Calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bold%20and%20archaic%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20the%20scheme%20does%20not%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%20evolving%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ecircumstances%20of%20the%20society.%20%26quot%3BThe%20old%20and%20archaic%20data%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20encompass%20the%20benefit%2C%20which%20would%20actually%20need%20to%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20This%20assumes%20great%20importance%20in%20view%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20various%20limiting%20factors%20in%20the%20scheme%20framed%20by%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%20which%20if%20applied%20along%20with%20the%202011%20data%20will%20render%20many%20people%20ineligible%20for%20benefits%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20even%20though%20they%20are%20being%20provided%20free%20medical%20services%20under%20the%20schemes%20formulated%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20scheme%20which%20is%20based%20upon%20an%20outdated%20data%20can%20by%20no%20stretch%20of%20imagination%20be%20thrust%20down%20the%20throat%20of%20any%20other%20government%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20AAP%20government%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20said%20there%20is%20no%20willingness%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20implement%20the%20central%20scheme.%20She%20clarified%20that%20the%20Centre's%20scheme%20was%20not%20to%20substitute%20the%20state%20government's%20initiatives%20but%20to%20support%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736837760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fqrkq57t_coronavirus-india-generic-hospital-generic-covid-hospital-reuters-650_625x300_10_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-2025-ayushman-bharat-cant-be-thrust-down-throat-delhis-aap-government-on-ayushman-bharat-7469669%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20has%20told%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20that%20it%20did%20not%20implement%20the%20Centre's%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Yojana%20for%20medical%20insurance%20because%20the%20capital's%20residents%20enjoy%20%26quot%3Bsuperior%26quot%3B%20benefits%20under%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20schemes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-2025-ayushman-bharat-cant-be-thrust-down-throat-delhis-aap-government-on-ayushman-bharat-7469669%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Game%20Changer%20struggles%20to%20cross%20US%20%241.9%20million%20collection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736837666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117226742%2Cimgsize-155164.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2