0the%20impact%20with%20the%20once%20and%20future%20president%2C%20according%20to%20Peter%20Loge%2C%20director%20of%20George%20Washington%20University's%20School%20of%20Media%20and%20Public%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20Musk%20is%20rich%2C%20and%20brash%2C%20and%20he%20is%20constantly%20reminding%20Donald%20Trump%20how%20wonderful%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20--%20which%20are%20all%20things%20Donald%20Trump%20likes%2C%26quot%3B%20Loge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECutting%20and%20slashing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Lorenzo%20Castellani%2C%20a%20history%20professor%20at%20Rome's%20Luiss%20Guido%20Carli%2C%20warns%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20chances%20of%20friction%20being%20generated%20in%20the%20long%20run%20are%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20been%20named%20in%20charge%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20slash%20federal%20spending%20and%20regulations.%20The%20ambitious%20plans%20are%20popular%20with%20right-wing%20ideologues%20but%20the%20Trump%20camp%20has%20not%20explained%20how%20such%20sweeping%20changes%20would%20avoid%20conflicts%20of%20interest%2C%20given%20that%20Musk%20is%20a%20major%20government%20contractor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20Trump's%20inauguration%20--%20he%20takes%20the%20oath%20on%20January%2020%20--%20Musk%20appears%20to%20be%20running%20into%20his%20first%20doses%20of%20political%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20boss%20had%20initially%20vowed%20to%20chop%20a%20highly%20improbable%20%242%20trillion%20in%20government%20spending%2C%20but%20now%20says%20%26quot%3Bwe've%20got%20a%20good%20shot%26quot%3B%20at%20saving%20%241%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20that%20would%20be%20a%20colossal%20undertaking%2C%20with%20the%20government's%20budget%20about%20%247%20trillion%20overall%20--%20making%20such%20dramatic%20cuts%20difficult%20without%20losing%20crucial%20services%20or%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20African%20native%2C%2053%2C%20has%20appeare