hief-succeeding-s-somanath-125011400134_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20also%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Level%20Human%20Rated%20Certification%20Board%20(HRCB)%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20programme%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fv-narayanan-assumes-charge-as-new-isro-chief-succeeding-s-somanath-125011400134_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22V%20Narayanan%20Assumes%20Charge%20As%20New%20ISRO%20Chief%2C%20Succeeds%20S%20Somanath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EV%20Narayanan%20has%20assumed%20charge%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20ISRO%2C%20replacing%20S%20Somanath%2C%20the%20Space%20Agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20ISRO%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDr%20V%20Narayanan%2C%20Distinguished%20Scientist%20(Apex%20Grade)%2C%20assumed%20the%20charge%20of%20Secretary%2C%20Department%20of%20Space%2C%20Chairman%2C%20Space%20Commission%20and%20Chairman%2C%20ISRO%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20January%2013%2C%202025.%26quot%3B%20Prior%20to%20this%2C%20Narayanan%20served%20as%20the%20Director%20of%20ISRO's%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20Systems%20Centre%20(LPSC)%2C%20a%20key%20facility%20responsible%20for%20the%20development%20of%20propulsion%20systems%20for%20launch%20vehicles%20and%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Level%20Human%20Rated%20Certification%20Board%20(HRCB)%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20programme%2C%20India's%20ambitious%20human%20spaceflight%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20veteran%20scientist%2C%20Narayanan%20joined%20ISRO%20in%201984%20and%20has%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20India's%20space%20missions%20over%20the%20decades.%20He%20became%20the%20Director%20of%20LPSC%20in%20January%202018%2C%20cementing%20his%20reputation%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20rocket%20and%20spacecraft%20propulsion%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarayanan%20hails%20from%20a%20humble%20background%20and%20is%20an%20alumnus%20of%20IIT%20Kharagpur%2C%20where%20he%20completed%20his%20M.Tech%20in%20Cryogenic%20Engineering%20and%20PhD%20in%20Aerospace%20Engineering.%20Awarded%20the%20Silver%20Medal%20for%20securing%20the%20first%20rank%20in%20his%20M.Tech%20programme%2C%20he%20has%20also%20received%20the%20Distinguished%20Alumni%20Award%20in%202018%20and%20the%20Life%20Fellowship%20Award%20in%202023%20from%20IIT%20Kharagpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20joining%20ISRO%2C%20Narayanan%20worked%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20at%20TI%20Diamond%20Chain%20Ltd.%2C%20Madras%20Rubber%20Factory%2C%20and%20Bharat%20Heavy%20Electricals%20Limited%20(BHEL)%20at%20Trichy%20and%20Ranipet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20his%2040-year%20tenure%20at%20ISRO%2C%20including%20seven%20years%20as%20Director%20of%20the%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20Systems%20Centre%20(LPSC)%2C%20he%20has%20made%20groundbreaking%20contributions%20to%20India's%20space%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20India%20was%20denied%20the%20cryogenic%20technology%20for%20GSLV%20Mk-ll%20vehicle%2C%20he%20designed%20the%20engine%20systems%2C%20developed%20necessary%20software%20tools%2C%20contributed%20for%20establishing%20the%20necessary%20infrastructure%20and%20test%20facilities%2C%20testing%20and%20qualification%20and%20completing%20the%20development%20of%20Cryogenic%20Upper%20Stage%20(CUS)%20and%20making%20it%20operational%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20project%20director%20of%20the%20C25%20cryogenic%20project%20for%20the%20LVM3%20vehicle%2C%20he%20led%20the%20development%20of%20the%20C25%20cryogenic%20stage%20powered%20by%20a%2020-tonne%20thrust%20engine%2C%20which%20was%20crucial%20for%20the%20successful%20maiden%20launch%20of%20LVM3.%20His%20M.Tech%20thesis%20and%20PhD%20work%20were%20instrumental%20in%20the%20development%20of%20these%20systems%2C%20making%20India%20one%20of%20only%20six%20countries%20with%20indigenous%20cryogenic%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarayanan%20played%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20India's%20lunar%20missions.%20For%20Chandryaan-2%20and%203%2C%20he%20led%20the%20development%20of%20the%20L110%20Liquid%20Stage%2C%20the%20C25%20Cryogenic%20Stage%2C%20and%20propulsion%20systems%20that%20enabled%20the%20spacecraft%20to%20reach%20the%20Moon's%20orbit%20and%20achieve%20a%20soft%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20PSLV%20C57%2FAditya%20L1%20mission%2C%20he%20oversaw%20the%20realisation%20of%20the%20second%20and%20fourth%20stages%2C%20control%20power%20plants%2C%20and%20the%20propulsion%20system%20that%20helped%20position%20the%20spacecraft%20in%20a%20halo%20orbit%20at%20L1%2C%20making%20India%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20successfully%20study%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarayanan%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20the%20Gaganyaan%20programme%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20human-rating%20of%20the%20LVM3%20vehicle%20and%20the%20development%20of%20various%20systems%2C%20including%20cryogenic%20stages%2C%20life%20support%20systems%2C%20and%20propulsion%20systems%20for%20the%20crew%20and%20service%20modules.%20He%20also%20chaired%20the%20Gaganyaan%20Certification%20Board%2C%20overseeing%20the%20certification%20process%20for%20multiple%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20his%20leadership%2C%20ISRO%20has%20advanced%20the%20development%20of%20next-generation%20propulsion%20systems%2C%20including%20a%20200-tonne%20thrust%20LOX-Kerosene%20semi-cryogenic%20rocket%20system%2C%20a%20110-tonne%20thrust%20LOX-Methane%20engine%2C%20and%20electric%20and%20green%20propulsion%20systems%20for%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20guided%20the%20propulsion%20systems%20for%20upcoming%20missions%20such%20as%20the%20Venus%20Orbiter%2C%20Chandrayaan-4%2C%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Antariksha%20Station%20(BAS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20Fellow%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Academy%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Aeron