ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fq3-fy25-company-results-today-jan-14-hdfc-amc-network18-125011400131_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Q3FY25%20company%20results%20today%3A%20Shopper%20Stop%2C%20SRM%20Energy%2C%20and%20Shree%20Pushkar%20Chemicals%20%26amp%3B%20Fertilisers%20will%20also%20be%20releasing%20their%20earnings%20report%20on%20January%2014%20for%20the%20quarter%20that%20ended%20on%20Dec%2031%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fq3-fy25-company-results-today-jan-14-hdfc-amc-network18-125011400131_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%2C100%20Bulls%20In%20Fray%2C%20Car%20On%20Prize%20List%3A%20Jallikattu%20Event%20Begins%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world-renowned%20three-day%20Jallikattu%20event%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Madurai%20kicked%20off%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20Avaniyapuram%20village%20holding%20its%20first-day%20event%20which%20features%201%2C100%20bulls%20and%20900%20bull-tamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20bull%20will%20be%20awarded%20a%20tractor%20worth%20Rs%2011%20lakhs%2C%20while%20the%20best%20bull-tamer%20will%20receive%20a%20car%20worth%20Rs%208%20lakhs%2C%20alongside%20other%20prizes.%20The%20other%20two%20Jallikattu%20events%20in%20Madurai%20will%20be%20held%20at%20Palamedu%20and%20Alanganallur%20on%20January%2015%20and%20January%2016%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrict%20rules%20and%20security%20measures%20are%20in%20place%20for%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20directions%20issued%20by%20the%20Madurai%20district%20administration%2C%20each%20bull%20can%20participate%20only%20in%20one%20of%20the%20three%20jallikattu%20competitions%20in%20the%20district.%20Each%20bull%20can%20be%20accompanied%20only%20by%20its%20owner%20and%20a%20trainer%20familiar%20with%20the%20bull.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBull%20tamers%20and%20owners%20of%20the%20bulls%20needed%20to%20register%20through%20the%20official%20district%20administration%20website%2C%20%26quot%3Bmadurai.nic.in%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20submitted%20documents%20were%20verified%20by%20the%20authorities.%20Only%20those%20deemed%20eligible%20have%20received%20a%20downloadable%20token%2C%20which%20is%20mandatory%20for%20participation.%20Without%20this%20token%2C%20neither%20bull%20tamers%20nor%20bulls%20are%20permitted%20to%20enter%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jallikattu%20events%20of%20Madurai%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20Alanganallur%2C%20are%20internationally%20recognized%20as%20a%20vibrant%20celebration%20of%20Tamil%20heritage%20and%20rural%20valour.%20With%20preparations%20in%20full%20swing%20and%20expectations%20running%20high%2C%20this%20year's%20competitions%20are%20set%20to%20attract%20significant%20participation%20and%20global%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Jallikattu%20event%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%202025%20was%20held%20on%20Saturday%20at%20Thachankurichi%20village%20in%20Pudukkottai%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPudukkottai%20district%20is%20known%20for%20having%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20vadivasal%20(entry%20points%20for%20bulls)%20and%20hosting%20the%20most%20Jallikattu%20events%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Between%20January%20and%20May%2031%2C%20over%20120%20Jallikattu%20events%2C%20more%20than%2030%20bullock%20cart%20races%2C%20and%20over%2050%20vadamadu%20(tethered%20bull)%20events%20are%20typically%20conducted%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJallikattu%20is%20an%20age-old%20bull-taming%20event%20celebrated%20mostly%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20as%20part%20of%20Pongal%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jallikattu%2C%20a%20bull%20is%20released%20into%20a%20crowd%20of%20people%2C%20and%20participants%20in%20the%20event%20try%20to%20grab%20the%20large%20hump%20on%20the%20bull's%20back%2C%20attempting%20to%20bring%20the%20bull%20to%20a%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20history%20of%20Jallikattu%20dates%20back%20to%20400-100%20BCE%2C%20when%20the%20Ayars%2C%20an%20ethnic%20group%20in%20India%2C%20played%20it.%20The%20name%20is%20coined%20from%20two%20words%3A%20Jalli%20(silver%20and%20gold%20coins)%20and%20Kattu%20(tied).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736826480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2F3995s7cs_jallikattu-pti_625x300_14_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1-100-bulls-in-fray-car-on-prize-list-jallikattu-event-begins-in-tamil-nadu-7468682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world-renowned%20three-day%20Jallikattu%20event%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Madurai%20kicked%20off%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20Avaniyapuram%20village%20holding%20its%20first-day%20event%20which%20features%201%2C100%20bulls%20and%20900%20bull-tamers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1-100-bulls-in-fray-car-on-prize-list-jallikattu-event-begins-in-tamil-nadu-7468682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Exploring%20Possible%20Sale%20Of%20US%20TikTok%20Operations%20To%20Elon%20Musk%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChinese%20officials%20are%20exploring%20a%20potential%20sale%20of%20US%20TikTok%20operations%20to%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20as%20the%20video-sharing%20platform%20faces%20an%20American%20law%20requiring%20imminent%20Chinese%20divestment%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20reported%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20citing%20anonymous%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20outlined%20one%20scenario%20being%20discussed%20in%20Beijing%20where%20Musk's%20social%20media%20company%20X%20would%20purchase%20TikTok%20from%20Chinese%20owner%20ByteDance%20and%20combine%20it%20into%20the%20platform%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20estimated%20the%20value%20of%20TikTok's%20US%20operations%20at%20between%20%2440%20and%20%2450%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Musk%20is%20currently%20ranked%20as%20the%20world's%20wealthiest%20person%2C%20Bloomberg%20said%20it%20was%20not%20clear%20how%20Musk%20could%20execute%20the%20transaction%2C%20or%20if%20he%20would%20need%20to%20sell%20other%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20passed%20a%20law%20last%20year%20that%20requires%20TikTok's%20ByteDance%20to%20either%20sell%20the%20wildly%20popular%20platform%20or%20shut%20it%20down.%20It%20goes%20into%20effect%20Sunday%20--%20a%20day%20before%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20takes%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20alleges%20TikTok%20allows%20Beijing%20to%20collect%20data%20and%20spy%20on%20users%20and%20is%20a%20conduit%20to%20spread%20propaganda.%20China%20and%20ByteDance%20strongly%20deny%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20has%20challenged%20the%20law%2C%20taking%20an%20appeal%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20heard%20oral%20arguments%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20hearing%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20conservative%20and%20liberal%20justices%20on%20the%20nine-member%20bench%20appeared%20skeptical%20of%20arguments%20by%20a%20lawyer%20for%20TikTok%20that%20forcing%20a%20sale%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20First%20Amendment%20free%20speech%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20characterized%20Beijing's%20consideration%20of%20a%20possible%20Musk%20transaction%20as%20%26quot%3Bstill%20preliminary%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%20Chinese%20officials%20have%20yet%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20how%20to%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20it%20was%20not%20clear%20how%20much%20ByteDance%20knew%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20an%20AFP%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20a%20representative%20was%20cited%20by%20Variety%20as%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20be%20expected%20to%20comment%20on%20pure%20fiction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20a%20close%20ally%20to%20Trump%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20play%20an%20influential%20role%20in%20Washington%20in%20the%20coming%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20runs%20electric%20car%20company%20Tesla%2C%20which%20has%20a%20major%20factory%20in%20China%20and%20counts%20the%20country%20as%20one%20of%20the%20automaker's%20biggest%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20enact%20new%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20which%20would%20expand%20a%20trade%20war%20begun%20in%20his%20first%20term%20and%20which%20was%20largely%20upheld%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20supplemented%2C%20by%20outgoing%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736826000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Faelkrtt_elon-musk_625x300_18_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-exploring-possible-sale-of-us-tiktok-operations-to-elon-musk-report-7468638%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%20officials%20are%20exploring%20a%20potential%20sale%20of%20US%20TikTok%20operations%20to%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20as%20the%20video-sharing%20platform%20faces%20an%20American%20law%20requiring%20imminent%20Chinese%20divestment%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20reported%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-exploring-possible-sale-of-us-tiktok-operations-to-elon-musk-report-7468638%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Glob