would%20I%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20I%20couldn't%20just%20quit%20my%20job%20without%20a%20plan.%20I%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20meaningful%20project%20to%20which%20I%20could%20devote%20my%20energies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20much%20thought%20and%20reflection%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20banking%20to%20run%20my%20own%20training%20institute%20for%20young%20professionals.%20I%20started%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiol.life%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstitute%20of%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202015%20with%20the%20mission%20of%20helping%20young%20people%20achieve%20success%20at%20work%20and%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245c97527-de7d-4d10-9990-32893ef17425%5C%22%3EFIRE%20isn't%20as%20great%20as%20you%20think%20it%20is%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eric%20Sim%20giving%20a%20speech%20to%20CFA%20Society%20members.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676240836c531c315b88e145%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESince%20leaving%20banking%2C%20Sim%20has%20become%20a%20professional%20speaker%20and%20executive%20coach.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20coauthored%20a%20book%20on%20career%20guidance%20called%20%26quot%3BSmall%20Actions.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEric%20Sim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20have%20achieved%20financial%20freedom%2C%20I'm%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Independence%20Retire%20Early%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20FIRE%2C%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20FIRE%2C%20you%20must%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20your%20income%20during%20your%20working%20years.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20people%20often%20don't%20have%20a%20clear%20idea%20of%20what%20retiring%20will%20look%20like%20for%20them%20or%20if%20they'll%20enjoy%20it%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20they're%20in%20the%20weeds%20and%20working%20toward%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20when%20you%20first%20retire%2C%20you%20can%20do%20whatever%20you%20want.%20You%20can%20travel%20overseas%2C%20hit%20the%20spa%2C%20or%20play%20golf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20for%2010%20to%2020%20years%2C%20being%20free%20from%20the%20grind%20for%20the%20first%20three%20months%20feels%20good.%20But%20you'll%20get%20bored%20very%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20are%20working%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20plan%20for%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do.%20Your%20day%20job%20will%20give%20you%20more%20than%20enough%20things%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20are%20financially%20independent%2C%20without%20a%20regular%20schedule%20to%20adhere%20to%2C%20you%20need%20to%20find%20projects%20to%20occupy%20your%20time.%20If%20you%20don't%20do%20that%2C%20then%20your%20days%20are%20wasted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223551d79-b8bd-46fe-8526-e4f012b4cd8d%5C%22%3EA%20good%20retirement%20isn't%20just%20about%20having%20money%20in%20the%20bank%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20have%20a%20good%20retirement%2C%20you%20will%20need%20three%20types%20of%20capital.%20Besides%20financial%20capital%2C%20you%20need%20human%20and%20social%20capital%20if%20you%20want%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20your%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuman%20capital%20refers%20to%20the%20knowledge%20you%20possess.%20You%20can%20build%20this%20up%20through%20your%20career%20or%20through%20your%20side%20hustles%20and%20hobbies.%20By%20developing%20your%20interests%20and%20skills%2C%20you%20will%20know%20what%20activities%20you%20want%20to%20do%20when%20you%20go%20into%20retirement%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20capital%20refers%20to%20the%20goodwill%20you%20accumulate%20with%20others.%20The%20small%20help%20that%20you%20offer%20to%20others%20can%20come%20back%20in%20a%20big%20way%20when%20you%20retire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20you%20need%20to%20know%20what%20yo