reate%20independent%20infrastructure%20around%20the%20AT%20Protocol%2C%20an%20open-source%20technology%20that%20powers%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fx-competitor-bluesky-valuation-new-funding-round-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBluesky%20social%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20allows%20anyone%20to%20build%20their%20own%20social%20media%20applications%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20open%20web%20protocols%20let%20anyone%20build%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20comes%20at%20a%20critical%20moment%20when%20traditional%20social%20platforms%20are%20facing%20intense%20scrutiny%20over%20their%20concentrated%20ownership%20and%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20we%20have%20a%20clear%20pathway%20to%20securing%20the%20future%20of%20social%20media%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20connection%2C%20creativity%2C%20and%20joy%2C%26quot%3B%20Nabiha%20Syed%2C%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Mozilla%20Foundation%20and%20one%20of%20nine%20custodians%20overseeing%20the%20project%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20will%20take%20community-driven%20resources%20and%20independent%20infrastructure%20to%20ensure%20it%20remains%20free%20from%20the%20pressures%20of%20venture%20capital%20and%20billionaire%20capture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign's%20immediate%20goal%20is%20to%20raise%20%244%20million%20as%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20%2430%20million%20three-year%20effort.%20The%20funds%20will%20be%20used%20to%20establish%20a%20public%20interest%20foundation%20supporting%20the%20AT%20Protocol%20and%20build%20independent%20infrastructure%20including%20a%20second%20%26quot%3Brelay%26quot%3B%20system.%20The%20relay%20is%20effectively%20a%20backup%20index%20of%20all%20content%20on%20the%20network%20that%20ensures%20developers%20and%20users%20can%20access%20posts%20even%20if%20Bluesky%20restricts%20access%20to%20its%20data.%20The%20capital%20will%20also%20be%20used%20to%20fund%20developers%20to%20create%20new%20applications%20on%20the%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20publishing%2C%20the%20campaign%20had%20raised%20nearly%20%2418%2C000%20from%20273%20donors%20on%20GoFundMe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Syed%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Foundation's%20key%20goals%20is%20to%20operate%20the%20AT%20Protocol%20infrastructure%20independently%20from%20Bluesky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20greater%20the%20number%20of%20stakeholders%20who%20build%20on%20AT%20Protocol%2C%20the%20more%20countervailing%20power%20they%20have%20with%20regards%20to%20Bluesky%20or%20any%20other%20large%20company%20involved%20in%20the%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Foundation%20will%20operate%20AT%20Protocol%20infrastructure%20independently%20from%20Bluesky%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20always%20an%20alternative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoger%20McNamee%2C%20an%20early%20Facebook%20investor%20turned%20tech%20critic%20who%20is%20backing%20the%20initiative%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20project%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20users%20are%20increasingly%20frustrated%20with%20existing%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20a%20world%20right%20now%20where%20every%20new%20startup%20is%20either%20crypto%20or%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20McNamee%20said.%20%26quot%3BShow%20me%20something%20that%20might%20actually%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place.%20If%20this%20works%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20much%20better%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20Bluesky%20has%20seen%20explosive%20growth.%20BI%20reported%20last%20week%20that%20the%20company%20is%20in%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fx-competitor-bluesky-valuation-new-funding-round-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraising%20new%20funding%20led%20by%20Bain%20Capital%20Ventures%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20value%20it%20at%20around%20%24700%20million.%20The%20platform%20reached%20nearly%2026%20million%20users%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20with%20nearly%20half%20joining%20in%20the%20last%20six%20weeks%20of%20the%20year%20following%20Donald%20Trump's%20election%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bluesky%20has%20positioned%20itself%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20X%2C%20Free%20Our%20Feeds'%20backers%20argue%20that%20even%20Bluesky's%20venture%20capital-backed%20structure%20could%20eventually%20face%20similar%20pressures%20as%20other%20commercial%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBluesky%20is%20built%20on%20values%20we%20share%2C%20by%20people%20we%20admire.%20However%2C%20founders%20are%20not%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20project's%20FAQ%20states.%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20come%20under%20the%20same%20pressure%20all%20businesses%20face%20to%20maximize%20return%20to%20their%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign's%20nine%20custodians%20include%20executives%20from%20Mozilla%2C%20the%20Social%20Web%20Foundation%2C%20and%20other%20nonprofit%20technology%20organizations.%20Development%20Gateway%2C%20a%20US%20nonprofit%20organization%2C%20will%20hold%20funds%20raised%20through%20the%20crowdfunding%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20the%20announcement%20comes%20just%20as%20Meta%20significantly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cuts-fact-checker-ties-by-march-leaked-meeting-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escaled%20back%20its%20fact-checking%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20as%20X%20continues%20to%20struggle%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-sues-twitch-advertising-boycott-lawsuit-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20exodus%20under%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20leadership.%20The%20initiative's%20backers%20argue%20that%20these%20recent%20developments%20highlight%20the%20risks%20of%20concentrated%20ownership%20of%20social%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20gone%20a%20really%20long%20