20in%20the%20US%20due%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-details-when-how-legal-cases-trump-options%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edivest-or-ban%20law%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20two%20other%20apps%20with%20Chinese%20owners%20have%20risen%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Apple%20app%20store%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-instagram-killer-xiaohongshu-explained-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXiaohongshu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20known%20as%20RedNote%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-lemon8-top-app-apple-app-store-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELemon8%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20app%20with%20the%20same%20owner%20as%20TikTok%2C%20hit%20the%20top%20two%20spots%20on%20the%20Apple%20app%20store%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXiaohongshu%20functions%20similarly%20to%20Instagram%2C%20but%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ecommerce-app-xiaohongshu-is-expanding-overseas-sources-say-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20commerce%20features%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20Lemon8%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-owner-bytedance-new-app-lemon8-paying-creators-to-post-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%20by%20creators%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20Pinterest-like%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rush%20to%20download%20these%20apps%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20head-scratcher%2C%20as%20they%20could%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20same%20divestment%20requirements%20as%20TikTok%20if%20the%20US%20government%20chooses%20to%20target%20them.%20The%20Protecting%20Americans%20from%20Foreign%20Adversary%20Controlled%20Applications%20Act%20applies%20to%20social%20platforms%20owned%20by%20countries%20that%20the%20US%20government%20views%20as%20foreign%20adversaries.%20TikTok%20became%20a%20political%20target%20because%20its%20owner%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20is%20based%20in%20China%2C%20which%20the%20US%20government%20has%20labeled%20a%20foreign%20adversary%20and%20Congress%20views%20as%20a%20national-security%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20is%20clearly%20subject%20to%20the%20divest-or-ban%20law%2C%20as%20it's%20named%20in%20the%20bill's%20text.%20But%20ByteDance%20is%20also%20named%2C%20which%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20why%20its%20other%20app%2C%20Lemon8%2C%20is%20suddenly%20surging%20in%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Krepich%2C%20the%20communications%20director%20for%20the%20House%20Committee%20on%20Energy%20and%20Commerce%2C%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fconormurray%2F2025%2F01%2F02%2Fwhat-to-know-about-tiktok-alternative-lemon8-and-whether-it-could-be-banned-too%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Forbes%20the%20bill%20would%20ban%20Lemon8%20unless%20ByteDance%20divested.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20committee%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider%20on%20whether%20it%20would%20apply%20to%20Xiaohongshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20was%20written%20broadly%20and%20could%20be%20enforced%20on%20any%20company%20owned%20by%20a%20foreign%20adversary%20that%20permits%20a%20user%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20an%20account%20or%20profile%20to%20generate%2C%20share%2C%20and%20view%20text%2C%20images%2C%20videos%2C%20real-time%20communications%2C%20or%20similar%20content.%26quot%3B%20That%20could%20include%20Xiaohongshu%20if%20the%20US%20government%20chose%20to%20target%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20does%20have%20some%20exceptions%2C%20including%20apps%20where%20users%20%26quot%3Bpost%20product%20reviews%2C%20business%20reviews%2C%20or%20travel%20information%20and%20reviews.%26quot%3B%20That%20suggests%20Chinese%20e-commerce%20platforms%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20would%20not%20be%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EByteDance%2C%20Xiaohongshu%2C%20Apple%2C%20and%20Google%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22683dfac7-182b-4005-86fa-37f787ce0a8a%5C%22%3EWhy%20users%20are%20flocking%20to%20these%20two%20apps%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20tough%20to%20say%20exactly%20what's%20driving%20mass%20interest%20in%20Xiaohongshu%20and%20Lemon8.%20Some%20users%20may%20be%20flocking%20to%20the%20apps%20to%20find%20a%20replacement%20for%20TikTok%2C%20while%20others%20may%20simply%20like%20their%20product%20features.%20In%20December%2C%20Xiaohongshu%20had%20around%20300%20million%20monthly%20active%20users%20globally%2C%20Bloomberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-12-12%2Fchina-s-instagram-style-xiaohongshu-crosses-1-billion-in-profit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20possibility%20for%20the%20downloads%20surge%20is%20that%20TikTok%20users%20are%20choosing%20the%20Chinese%20apps%20as%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20protest%20of%20the%20divest-or-ban%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20is%20just%20retaliation%20towards%20the%20government%20in%20the%20simplest%20way%2C%20but%20in%20a%20way%20that%20feels%20very%20native%20to%20Gen%20Z%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Meagan%20Loyst%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20investor%20collective%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-vc-meagan-loyst-venture-capital-survey-young-investors-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20VCs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20millennials%20pioneered%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchallenge-accepted-instagram-trend-turkey-istanbul-convention-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslacktivism%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20with%20online%20petitions%2C%20Gen%20Z%20seems%20to%20be%20trying%20something%20new.%20You%20might%20call%20it%20%26quot%3Btrolltivism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20trolling%20on%20a%20