%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC8uH-ZxyAWY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Jaagir%20Manor%2C%20Dudhwa%20%E2%80%93%20IHCL%20SeleQtions%20(%40jaagirmanor)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20well%20before%20hunting%20was%20outlawed%20in%201972.%20The%20jungle%20formed%20a%20prized%20destination%20for%20hunting%20expeditions.%20And%20the%20family%20would%20often%20join%20in%3B%20Billy%20Arjan%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20boy%E2%80%99s%20targets%20were%20small%20animals%2C%20scurrying%20to%20escape%20his%20watchful%20eye.%20But%20as%20he%20grew%20older%2C%20his%20targets%20matured%20too.%20Soon%2C%20he%20was%20aiming%20at%20owlets%2C%20hyaenas%2C%20leopards%2C%20and%20tigers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20more%20compelling%20than%20the%20%3Cem%3Eshikari%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(hunter)%20exploits%20is%20the%20story%20of%20his%20redemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilly%20Arjan%20recalls%20his%20forties%20as%20the%20last%20time%20he%20picked%20up%20a%20rifle.%20As%20he%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20finally%20stopped%20shooting%20in%201960%20when%20I%20was%20overcome%20with%20remorse%20for%20ending%20the%20life%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343873%2Fwildlife-photographer-naturalist-in-ladakh-karamjeet-singh-snow-leopards-himalayan-brown-bear-endangered-species%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20beautiful%20leopard%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20headlights%20of%20my%20jeep.%20I%20had%20no%20right%20whatsoever%20to%20destroy%20what%20I%20could%20not%20create.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETapping%20on%20this%20sentiment%2C%20he%20gravitated%20to%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20%E2%80%94%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnknowst%20to%20many%2C%20this%20spur-of-the-moment%20decision%20went%20on%20to%20have%20an%20outsized%20impact%20on%20the%20future%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20wildlife%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20life%20dedicated%20to%20the%20tigers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20poignancy%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20Brinda%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20%5BBilly%20Arjan%5D%20shot%20the%20leopard%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20light%20in%20its%20eyes%20go%20out.%20That%20was%20the%20moment%20he%20was%20converted.%20He%20realised%20it%20was%20a%20dreadful%20thing%20to%20do%3B%20a%20cruel%20sport.%20He%20became%20extremely%20sorrowful%2C%20almost%20like%20an%20epiphany.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20he%20became%20a%20conservationist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20buzzword%20today%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20conservation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewasn%E2%80%99t%20understood%20as%20well%20in%20the%201960s.%20But%20Billy%20Arjan%20led%20the%20revolution%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Tiger%20Haven%E2%80%99%2C%20standing%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20present-day%20Dudhwa%20Tiger%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20350px)%20100vw%2C%20350px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Billy%20Arjan%20Singh%20had%20a%20fascination%20for%20tigers%20and%20spent%20four%20decades%20ensuring%20they%20were%20well%20protected.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821.jpg%20350w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-393048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBilly%20Arjan%20Singh%20had%20a%20fascination%20for%20tigers%20and%20spent%20four%20decades%20ensuring%20they%20were%20well%20protected%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftigerhavensociety.org%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiger%20Haven%20Society%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20inception%20of%20Tiger%20Haven%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%20how%20the%20summer%20of%201959%20was%20an%20unforgettable%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20gone%20out%20into%20the%20forest%20on%20Bhagwan%20Piari%2C%20the%20elephant%20with%20whom%20I%20spent%2025%20wonderful%20years.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20Himalayan%20ranges%20across%20the%20Dudhwa%20grasslands.%20At%20the%20confluence%20of%20the%20Soheli%20and%20Neora%20rivers%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20patch%20of%20land%20that%20was%20owned%20by%20a%20politician%20who%20had%20lost%20all%20interest%20in%20it.%20I%20bought%20it%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20functioning%20farm.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come%2C%20the%20farm%20went%20through%20a%20transmutation%20of%20sorts%20and%20became%20a%20haven%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F279646%2Fbest-wildlife-photography-destinations-india-kaziranga-kabini-ranthambore-kaziranga%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20was%20allowed%20to%20thrive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20him%2C%20this%20act%20felt%20like%20%E2%80%9Clike%20repaying%20old%20debts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeconding%20this%20narrative%20of%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20tigers%20is%20Samir%20Sinha%20IFS%2C%20who%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20WWF-India%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BBilly%20Arjan%5D%20held%20very%20strong%20views%20and%20would%20regularly%20type%20away%20letters%20on%20his%20trusty%20typewriter%20to%20flag%20his%20concerns%20on%20issues%20that%20he%20considered%20important.%20Though%20his%20prolific%20writing%20was%20curtailed%20due%20to%20the%20physical%20effort%20of%20typing%20in%20his%20last%20years%2C%20even%20with%20failing%20health%2C%20his%20eyes%20would%20light%20up%20at%20the%20mention%20of%20the%20tiger%2C%20and%20he%20was%20always%20eager%20to%20engage%20in%20efforts%20in%20support%20of%20this%20majestic%20animal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinha%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20years%20succeeding%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20Dudhwa%20where%20he%20began%20his%20work%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333222%2Fanne-wright-conservationist-wildlife-protection-act-reserves-project-tiger-legacy-raza-kazmi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiger%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20years%20were%20coloured%20with%20experiments%20and%20accolades%20%E2%80%94%20navigating%20through%20waves%20of%20conflict%20posed%20by%20communities%20who%20depended%20on%20the%20game%20and%20stepping%20closer%20to%20his%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Bring%20Dudhwa%20under%20Project%20Tiger%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20the%20conservation%20of%20tigers%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20breathe%20easy%20until%20he%20had%20pulled%20out%20all%20the%20stops.%20And%20the%20story%20of%20how%20he%20compelled%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20consider%20protecting%20the%20forests%20of%20Dudhwa%20puts%20this%20never-die-spirit%20into%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrinda%20tells%20me%20that%20the%20duo%20would%20often%20correspond%20with%20each%20other%20through%20postcards.%20She%20then%20proceeds%20to%20read%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Duff%20Hart-Davis%E2%80%99%20biography%2C%20which%20confirms%20the%20story%20of%20Billy%20Arjan%20standing%20up%20to%20bureaucracy%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20safeguard%20the%20tigers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20350px)%20100vw%2C%20350px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Billy%20Arjan%20Singh%20petitioned%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20bring%20the%20forests%20of%20Dudhwa%20under%20Project%20Tiger%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917.jpg%20350w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-393052%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBilly%20Arjan%20Singh%20petitioned%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20bring%20the%20forests%20of%20Dudhwa%20under%20Project%20Tiger%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftigerhavensociety.org%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiger%20Haven%20Society%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20excerpt%20details%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%201969%20General%20Assembly%20of%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20the%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20where%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368687%2Fworld-animal-welfare-day-remembering-pioneers-wildlife-conservation-india-project-tiger%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecline%20in%20tiger%20populations%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20stressed.%20The%20assembly%20went%20on%20to%20pass%20a%20resolution%20proposing%20a%20moratorium%20on%20hunting%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20income%20earned%20by%20%3Cem%3Eshikar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(hunting)%20companies%20in%20the%20past%20should%20be%20replaced%20by%20straightforward%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20resolution%20swiftly%20put%20paid%20to%2026%20hunting%20firms%20which%20were%20too%20high%20bound%20to%20transfer%20their%20activities%20into%20tourism%20and%20went%20out%20of%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20biography%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20began%20to%20petition%20Indira%20Gandhi%20about%20the%20plight%20of%20wildlife%20in%20India%20and%20his%20beloved%20Dudhwa%20in%20particular.%20%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20in%201972%2C%20the%20Government%20passed%20the%20Indian%20Wildlife%20Act%20which%20at%20last%20set%20realistic%20schedules%20and%20penalties%2C%20and%20in%20September%20that%20year%2C%20the%20World%20Wildlife%20Fund%20launched%20Operation%20Tiger%2C%20a%20global%20fundraising%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20Brinda%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeaving%20a%20legacy%20behind%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilly%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20belief%20in%20tigers%20being%20crucial%20to%20existence%20is%20an%20article%20of%20faith.%20In%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%20Dudhwa%20became%20a%20safe%20haven%20where%20he%20lived%20until%20his%20death%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F234711%2Fhow-does-india-protect-tigers-fateh-singh-rathore-ranthambhore-national-park-rajasthan-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20sanctuary%20for%20the%20wildlife%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20had%20devoted%20his%20life%20to%20saving.%20He%20was%20a%20multifaceted%20powerhouse%20who%20lived%20his%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20passed%20away%20on%201%20January%202010%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2092%2C%20but%20not%20before%20changing%20the%20script%20of%20conservation%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20salute%20to%20his%20resolve%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%201995%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20gold%20medal%20by%20the%20World%20Wildlife%20Fund%20(1996).%20In%201997%2C%20he%20became%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20Order%20of%20the%20Golden%20Ark%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Dutch%20order%20of%20merit%3B%20in%202004%20he%20won%20the%20J.Paul%20Getty%20Wildlife%20Conservation%20Award%3B%20and%20in%202006%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%2C%20and%20the%20Yash%20Bharati%20Award.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fphoto%252F%253Ffbid%253D456683486504283%2526set%253Da.456683459837619%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20glint%20of%20the%20awards%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20Billy%20Arjan%20had%20each%20time%20a%20tiger%20lived%20because%20of%20his%20efforts.%20Today%2C%20the%20landscape%20of%20Dudhwa%20National%20Park%20%E2%80%94%20a%20490%20sq%20km%20park%20established%20in%201977%2C%20which%20connects%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F223054%2Fkerala-forest-department-tiger-sreenivasan-earth-hero-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportant%20tiger%20habitats%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20India%20and%20Nepal%20%E2%80%94%20is%20decorated%20with%20elephants%2C%20rhinos%2C%20over%2045%20species%20of%20birds%20and%20of%20course%2C%20tigers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommending%20his%20passion%2C%20Brinda%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20always%20knew%20him%20as%20a%20person%20of%20tremendous%20belief.%20We%20were%20always%20proud%20of%20him.%E2%80%9D%20Brinda%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20at%20Tiger%20Haven%20Society%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20champion%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20life%2C%20why%20anyone%20would%20want%20to%20hunt%20down%20an%20animal%20that%20is%20the%20core%20of%20the%20ecosystem%20was%20an%20enigma%20to%20him.%20And%2C%20till%20his%20last%20breath%2C%20he%20maintained%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20air%20we%20breathe%20and%20the%20water%20we%20drink%20stem%20from%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20universal%20environment%20and%20its%20economics.%20The%20tiger%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20truth.%20If%20it%20goes%2C%20we%20go.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESpecial%20thanks%20to%20Amith%20Bangre%2C%20General%20Manager%20and%20Chief%20Naturalist%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjaagirmanor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJaagir%20Manor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20his%20invaluable%20support%20in%20arranging%20interviews%20and%20providing%20crucial%20assistance%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wwfindia.org%2F%3F3880%2FTiger-walla-departs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Billy%E2%80%99%20Arjan%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20the%20legendary%20%E2%80%98Tiger-walla%E2%80%99%20departs%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20WWF%20India%2C%20Published%20on%206%20January%202010.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanctuarynaturefoundation.org%2Farticle%2Fmeet-billy-arjan-singh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeet%20Billy%20Arjan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Sanctuary%20Asia%2C%20Published%20in%20September%202000.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.naturesafariindia.com%2Fconservationists-in-india%2Fbilly-arjan-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBilly%20Arjan%20Singh%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Nature%20Safari%20India.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736403316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D393021%22%2C%22sum