B%20%E2%80%9CThe%20happiest%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori.%20However%2C%20this%20happiness%2C%20too%2C%20would%20be%20blemished%20by%20a%20tragedy.%20In%201985%2C%20Dutta%20lost%20his%20life%20in%20a%20jet%20crash.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20was%20forced%20to%20become%20a%20sex%20worker%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20was%20not%20easy%20after%20Dutta%E2%80%99s%20death.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20best%20part%20of%20my%20life%20and%20losing%20him%20was%20something%20I%20could%20not%20handle%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Noori%2C%20who%20had%20to%20process%20this%20immense%20grief%20with%20no%20shoulder%20to%20cry%20on.%20While%20she%20wanted%20to%20lead%20a%20respectable%20life%20alone%2C%20society%20would%20show%20no%20kindness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20forced%20to%20become%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334508%2Finspiring-story-of-sex-worker-turned-artist-aravani-art-project-for-transgenders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20sex%20worker%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20nobody%20was%20ready%20to%20employ%20me%20for%20other%20jobs.%20I%20needed%20to%20survive%2C%20and%20this%20job%20provided%20me%20with%20the%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20affirms.%20Outside%20the%20social%20stigma%2C%20her%20profession%20also%20came%20with%20serious%20health%20consequences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESexually%20transmitted%20diseases%20were%20common%20among%20sex%20workers%2C%20and%20Noori%20often%20assisted%20them%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267251%2Fvaccinate-sex-workers-transgenders-domestic-help-free-covidactioncollab-coronavirus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20medical%20help%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20one%20such%20visit%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20Noori%20saw%20a%20poster%20on%20HIV%20and%20AIDS%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20get%20tested%