0provides%20a%20comfortable%20home%20for%20children%20who%20have%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20are%20brought%20in%20by%20their%20parents%2C%20some%20are%20abandoned%2C%20and%20some%20are%20sent%20from%20hospitals%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20been%20able%20to%20save%20over%20400%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277718%2Fnakshatra-changemaker-inspiring-transwoman-bengaluru-destitute-orphans-ngo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20affected%20by%20HIV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20helped%20them%20with%20education%2C%20medicines%2C%20food%2C%20shelter%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20love%20and%20affection.%20Noori%20has%20invested%20in%20a%20space%20worth%20Rs%203%20crore%20for%20the%20children.%20%E2%80%9CI%20haven%E2%80%99t%20saved%20anything%20for%20myself.%20All%20I%20do%20right%20now%20is%20for%20them%20and%20their%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNoori%20%3Cem%3Eaaya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grandma)%20has%20always%20prioritised%20education%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20study%20three%20degrees%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Naga%20Thejas%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20at%20SIP%20Memorial%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20social%20work%2C%20hoping%20to%20start%20his%20own%20NGO%20to%20support%20people%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20600px)%20100vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Activities%20conducted%20for%20the%20children%20at%20the%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust%20provides%20a%20comfortable%20home%20for%20children%20who%20have%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20comfortable%20at%20SIP%20home%20as%20I%20used%20to%20get%20healthy%20and%20delicious%20meals%20every%20day.%20I%20also%20had%20my%20friends%2C%20with%20whom%20time%20would%20fly%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naga%2C%20sharing%20the%20joy%20of%20growing%20in%20the%20safe%20space%20created%20by%20Noori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20proud%20to%20say%20that%20I%20am%20the%20first%20transgender%20to%20own%20a%20passport%20and%20a%20ration%20card%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori%2C%20who%20currently%20holds%2022%20leadership%20positions%20for%20multiple%20organisations%20and%20welfare%20boards.%20She%20has%20been%20the%20Coordinator%20of%20the%20South%20Asia%20TIDES%20Foundation%20(2005%20to%202008)%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Transgender%20Welfare%20Board%20(2008)%2C%20and%20Vice%20President%20of%20India%20People%20Alliance%20Combating%20HIV%2FAIDS%20(IPACHA)%2C%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20society%20is%20more%20inclusive%20and%20aware%20of%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20transgenders%20and%20people%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20HIV.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20medical%20advancements%20help%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20physical%20aspects%2C%20and%20a%20comparatively%20understanding%20society%20makes%20the%20battles%20a%20little%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Naga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357165%2Fpalawi-project-hiv-positive-children-shelter-home-care-education-kids-mangal-shah-tai-maharashtra-empower-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20fear%20HIV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20advises.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20unfair%20to%20abandon%20your%20child%20simply%20because%20they%20have%20tested%20positive.%20I%E2%80%99m%20living%20proof%20that%20HIV%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20death%20sentence.%20All%20you%20need%20is%20the%20right%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Noori%20Mohammad%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736170030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled_5e478eaebfe30-1734611076.webp%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D390947%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noori%20Mohammad's%20journey%20is%20a%20powerful%20example%20of%20love%20and%20persistence.%20After%20enduring%20rejection%2C%20abuse%2C%20and%20the%20heartbreaking%20loss%20of%20her%20partner%2C%20she%20found%20strength%20in%20helping%20others.%20Today%2C%20her%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust%20provides%20a%20safe%20home%20for%20over%20400%20HIV-positive%20children%2C%20offering%20them%20love%2C%20education%2C%20and%20the%20hope%20of%20a%20brighter%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F390947%2Fnoori-mohammad-abuse-transwoman-hiv-positive-india-children-shelter%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Mushroom%20Farming%20Business%20Makes%20Rs%202%20Lakh%2FMonth%20%26amp%3B%20Trains%2010000%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20faced%20many%20challenges%2C%20but%20I%20never%20let%20them%20deter%20me.%20No%20matter%20how%20tough%20things%20got%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20could%20make%20it%20work.%20I%20just%20had%20to%20keep%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pratibha%20Jha%2C%2040%2C%20whose%20journey%20holds%20true%20the%20statement%20that%20with%20focused%20effort%2C%20anything%20is%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bihar%2C%20a%2010-year-old%20Pratibha%20would%20often%20watch%20local%20farmers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380434%2Ftrupti-dhakate-mushroom-farming-sustainable-eco-friendly-women-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivate%20mushrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20curious%20about%20how%20mushrooms%20grew%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CSomething%20about%20it%20fascinated%20me%2C%20but%20I%20never%20thought%20it%20could%20be%20my%20livelihood%20one%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20life%20took%20a%20sudden%20turn%20when%20her%20father%20passed%20away%2C%20and%20at%20the%20young%20age%20of%2015%2C%20she%20was%20married%20off%20to%20an%20engineer%20from%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Darbhanga.%20After%20moving%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20Mirzapur%20Hansi%20village%2C%20her%20interest%20in%20mushroom%20farming%20lingered%2C%20but%20the%20practicalities%20of%20starting%20a%20business%20seemed%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20spoke%20to%20people%20in%20my%20village%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335596%2Fmushroom-farming-business-tips-odisha-man-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20it%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits.%20Even%20her%20in-laws%2C%20who%20were%20%E2%80%9Cconservative%20and%20sceptical%20of%20women%20working%20outside%20the%20home%E2%80%9D%2C%20could%20not%20see%20value%20in%20what%20she%20wanted%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Pratibha%20was%20determined%20to%20follow%20her%20passion%20for%20mushroom%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20told%20my%20husband%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20mushroom%20farming.%20He%20admitted%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20much%20about%20it%20either%2C%20but%20I%20expressed%20my%20desire%20to%20carve%20out%20my%20own%20identity%20beyond%20the%20traditional%20role%20of%20a%20housewife%2C%20and%20he%20wholeheartedly%20supported%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHumble%20beginnings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20little%20knowledge%20and%20even%20fewer%20resources%2C%20Pratibha%20decided%20to%20shape%20her%20identity%20in%20this%20field.%20In%202015%2C%20she%20went%20to%20the%20Darbhanga%20Agriculture%20Department%20to%20inquire%20about%20training%2C%20but%20they%20directed%20her%20to%20Bihar%20Agricultural%20University%20(BAU)%2C%20Sabor%20University%2C%20in%20Bhagalpur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20I%20saw%20an%20ad%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F89391%2Fhow-organisation-use-mushroom-cultivation-empower%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%20farming%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20when%20I%20contacted%20them%2C%20they%20said%20that%20the%20course%20was%20over%20and%20I%20should%20try%20next%20year.%20So%20I%20w